rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear that a newfangled vehicle has
been constructed right here in Iira!

rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0002
rows.name:
It seems to be a massive craft that can
traverse the Cloud Sea even without the
power of a Divine Beast...

rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Apparently palace soldiers and local
engineers worked together to build it.
It was only completed recently.

rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It had some sort of name, but what
was it? Something with "mo"...?
"Mo"... "Mo"... Well, something like that.

rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm sure they could have used my help,
but I have no time for such things.
I always put my own inventions first!

rows.label: tlk70000017_05_msg0006
rows.name:
They begged me to help, of course,
but I turned them down - twice!
Gah hah hah!
